ng_page/template_background/268082/62c6b252b4be909511ff40202222f353.jpg&#39;); background-position: center center;"></div><div class="pko-story-box__content"><div class="pko-story-box__tags-and-category"><div class="pko-story-box__category" itemprop="articleSection">About Bank</div></div><h3 class="pko-story-box__title" style="overflow: hidden;">PKO Bank Polski, European Leader in Digital Banking</h3><div class="pko-story-box__date">2023.05.31</div><div class="pko-story-box__hover"><div class="pko-story-box__lead">PKO Bank Polski secured the first position in the 2023 Finnoscore ranking, establishing itself as the European leader in digital banking. The rankings, which assessed the digital maturity of 230 banks from Europe and North America, recognized PKO Bank Polski&#39;s excellence...</div><div class="pko-story-box__bottom"><div class="pko-story-box__social"><object class="pko-story-box__social-item"><a target="_blank" alt="twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=https://en.media.pkobp.pl/268082-pko-bank-polski-european-leader-in-digital-banking"><i class="ion-social-twitter"></i></a></object><object class="pko-story-box__social-item"><a target="_blank" class="" alt="facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://en.media.pkobp.pl/268082-pko-bank-polski-european-leader-in-digital-banking"><i class="ion-social-facebook"></i></a></object><object class="pko-story-box__social-item"><a target="_blank" class="" alt="linkedin" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://en.media.pkobp.pl/268082-pko-bank-polski-european-leader-in-digital-banking"><i class="ion-social-linkedin"></i></a></object></div></div></div></div></div></a><a class="grid__box-1-1" target="_self" href="/268084-first-virtual-job-fair-pkobanktalentow-in-the-metaverse"><div class="pko-story-box" itemscope="" itemtype="//schema.org/Article"><div class="pr-story__background" 